\noindent\textbf{Naming.} \emph{TensorStore} denotes this paper's checkpoint-loading system (Rust crate \texttt{tensor\_store}, Python \texttt{tensor\_store\_py}).\par
\noindent It is not affiliated with Google's TensorStore library for N-dimensional array storage.\par
